description: Updates the IPSet specified by the IPSet ID.

parameters.name: DetectorId
parameters.description: The detectorID that specifies the GuardDuty service whose IPSet you want to update. To find the detectorId in the current Region, see the Settings page in the GuardDuty console, or run the ListDetectors API.

parameters.name: IpSetId
parameters.description: The unique ID that specifies the IPSet that you want to update.
